skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: world smartz
des: Invocation Name: World Smartz. Say Alexa, start world smartz or Alexa, open woeld smartz, or just Alexa, world smartz. These will start a multiple choice quiz of 5 questions. These questions will be displayed on Echo Show and Echo Spot. Your answer must include the number of your choice. Other key phrases are "repeat, skip, stop, I don't know that one." You are given the correct answer if your choice was incorrect and the score is tallied.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
